{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Rescue Your Fellow Gobs</strong></h2><br>Join the Discord: <br>All Goblins have gone into hiding. Leave no stone unturned. Smash pots, crypts, and other things they might be hiding in. Lead them in the struggle for Goblinkind. All for Gob and Gob for all.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538120/extras/steamRescueGob.gif?t=1737664420\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Become A Loot Goblin</strong></h2><br><br>Open every chest you see and grab every piece of junk that you can get your little, gobby mitts on. Blast everything that moves and stockpile shiny rocks to become a walking trash can of annihilation.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538120/extras/steamGobLoot.gif?t=1737664420\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Run For Cover</strong></h2><br><br>Duck behind, on, or around pillars and boulders. Use every advantage to survive swarms of enemies while everything crumbles around you. Don't stop moving; Find new cover or be left in ruin.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538120/extras/steamCoverGob.gif?t=1737664420\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gob. Glory. Repeat.</strong></h2><br><br>Face the abyss over and over again. Never relent. Pick up your crown as many times as it takes. Come back stronger every time. More stats. More items. More Gobs.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538120/extras/steamDeadgeGob.gif?t=1737664420\" /><br><br>Join the Discord: ","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737664420","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538120/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737664420","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.stea